WEBVTT

00:00.121 --> 00:04.679
The word "These" tells us about two or more close things.

00:06.371 --> 00:07.683
These are animals.

00:09.356 --> 00:11.155
These are potatoes.

00:12.951 --> 00:14.887
These animals are wolves.

00:16.581 --> 00:18.445
These things are potatoes.

00:20.273 --> 00:24.841
The word "Those" tells us about two or more things far away.

00:26.633 --> 00:28.138
Those are animals.

00:29.900 --> 00:31.671
Those animals are penguins.

00:33.344 --> 00:35.391
Those places are stores.

